# Storefronts

**Object**

A resource object that represents a storefront, an Apple Music and iTunes Store territory that the content is available in.

## Declaration

```swift
object Storefronts
```

## Discussion

For the specification of language tags, see [https://help.apple.com/itc/musicspec/?lang=en#/itc740f60829] in iTunes Package Music Specification.
